		{
			"eventType": "comment",
			"text": "Initialize cutscene dialogue array (cutscene_n_dialogue object) on startup.\nThis array is an x by y array, where:\n- x (ie width) is the total dialogue count of this cutscene\n- y (ie height) is the number of attributes to keep track of per dialogue \n   - y = 3 for now, we keep track of text, current speaking position, and character name per dialogue\n      - (x, 0) stores text, (x, 1) stores current speaking character's position, (x, 2) stores character name"
		},
